## Roadmap

See `ROADMAP.md` (or the main issue tracker) for upcoming modules:
- Astronomy (astro)
- Chemistry (chem)
- Genetics & evolution (bio)
- Mechanics & orbits (mech)
- Relativity (relativity)

---

## Contributing
1. Add a new module under `science_ops/tools/yourtool.py`
2. Make a `typer.Typer()` instance in that file
3. Mount it in `cli.py` via `app.add_typer(...)`
4. Add tests in `tests/`
5. Open a PR

